<i>noun</i>: 채찍 [채찍], 채 [채], 매 [매] <i>verb</i>: 휘젓다 [휘젇따 ], 후려치다 [후려치다], 후려갈기다 [후려갈기다], 채찍질하다 [채찍찔하다], 매질하다 [매질하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>채찍 [채찍]</dt><br>
<dd>whip</dd><br>
<dd>가느다란 막대기의 끝에 노끈이나 가죽끈을 달아 말이나 소를 때려 모는 데 쓰는 물건.</dd><br>
<dd>A tool made by attaching strings or leather strips to the tip of a stick that is used for whipping and driving horses or cattle.</dd><br>
<dt>채 [채]</dt><br>
<dd>1. chae</dd><br>
<dd>팽이나 공 등을 치는 데에 쓰는 도구.</dd><br>
<dd>stick; racket: An implement used to spin a top or hit a ball, etc., with.</dd><br>
<dd>2. stick</dd><br>
<dd>벌로 사람을 때리는 데에 쓰는 얇은 막대기.</dd><br>
<dd>A thin rod used to spank people for punishment.</dd><br>
<dd>3. whip</dd><br>
<dd>가느다란 막대기의 끝에 노끈이나 가죽끈을 달아 말이나 소를 때려 모는 데 쓰는 물건.</dd><br>
<dd>A tool made by attaching strings or leather strips to the tip of a stick that is used for whipping and driving horses or cattle.</dd><br>
<dd>4. chae</dd><br>
<dd>북, 장구, 꽹과리, 징 등의 타악기를 치거나 현악기를 타서 소리를 내게 하는 도구.</dd><br>
<dd>stick: An implement used to play percussion or string instruments such as the buk, a barrel drum, janggu, an hourglass-shaped drum, kkwaenggwari, a small gong, jing, a larger gong, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>매 [매]</dt><br>
<dd>whip; rod</dd><br>
<dd>사람이나 짐승을 때리는 막대기. 또는 그것으로 때리는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A stick with which to beat a person or animal, or the act of beating with such a stick.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>휘젓다 [휘젇따 ]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stir; churn; whip; whisk</dd><br>
<dd>골고루 섞이도록 이리저리 마구 젓다.</dd><br>
<dd>To stir something from side to side wildly to mix it throughly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. stir; sweep</dd><br>
<dd>마구 뒤흔들어 어지럽게 만들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To shake someone or something up to make him/her confused or chaotic.</dd><br>
<dd>3. shake; swing; wave</dd><br>
<dd>이리저리 심하게 흔들어 젓다.</dd><br>
<dd>To move one's arms back and forth or shake one's head wildly.</dd><br>
<dt>후려치다 [후려치다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. slap; whip; strike; punch</dd><br>
<dd>주먹이나 채찍 등을 휘둘러 힘껏 때리거나 치다.</dd><br>
<dd>To slap or hit another person hard, wielding a whip or throwing a punch.</dd><br>
<dd>2. bargain to a knockdown price; drive a hard bargain</dd><br>
<dd>물건값을 너무 심하게 깎다.</dd><br>
<dd>To try to bargain something down to an excessively low price.</dd><br>
<dt>후려갈기다 [후려갈기다]</dt><br>
<dd>slap; whip; strike; punch</dd><br>
<dd>채찍이나 주먹 등을 휘둘러 힘껏 치거나 때리다.</dd><br>
<dd>To slap or hit another hard, wielding a whip or throwing a punch.</dd><br>
<dt>채찍질하다 [채찍찔하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. whip; lash</dd><br>
<dd>채찍으로 때리다.</dd><br>
<dd>To beat a person or animal with a whip.</dd><br>
<dd>2. whip</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 몹시 재촉하여 다그치거나 힘이 나도록 북돋아 주다.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) To rush or encourage to raise one's spirits by pressing.</dd><br>
<dt>매질하다 [매질하다]</dt><br>
<dd>whip; spank</dd><br>
<dd>매로 때리다.</dd><br>
<dd>To beat someone with a whip, a rod etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>